N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 65.28 - Failure to file a pleading

State Regulations

Failure to file any pleading pursuant to these rules when
due, may at the discretion of the Board, constitute a waiver of the right to
further participation in the proceeding. Notes
